\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {6}{\ignorespaces Clean vs. Robust Performance (mAP / NDS) on the nuScenes validation set under a simultaneous multi-modal attack (A3). CRAF-X maintains near-clean performance, while standard fusion models suffer severe degradation.}}{9}{}\protected@file@percent }
